PostgreSQL Setup : Mac Edition
content: PostgreSQL, also known as Postgres, is a free and open-source relational database management system emphasizing extensibility and technical standards compliance. It is designed to handle a range of workloads, from single machines to data warehouses or Web services with many concurrent users. Click here to know more: https://medium.com/next-gen-explorer/postgresql-setup-mac-edition-c5e3acb4b877
